com.saic.uicds.core.em.service

Interface MapService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MapServiceImpl

    @Transactional
public interface MapService
    The Map Service manages Layer and MapViewContext type work products. It also can pull all the features from a Shapefile and create Feature type work products for each of them. Each Feature type work product is then available via an WMS layer that is automatically added to the default Map that is created for every incident.
    Author:
    Patrick Neal - Image Matters, LLC
